et.asp?id=1610  WASPS: Breaking Ground for Today's Female USAF Pilots]\n* [http://www.nationalmuseum.af.mil/factsheets/factsheet.asp?id=1563  Women's Auxiliary Ferrying Squadron]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070831124822/http://www.nationalmuseum.af.mil/factsheets/factsheet.asp?id=1557  Nancy Harkness Love Biography]\n* [http://www.nationalmuseum.af.mil/factsheets/factsheet.asp?id=1541  Description of Fifinella from USAF website]\n* [http://www.nationalmuseum.af.mil/factsheets/factsheet.asp?id=1515  WASPS Demonstrate their Abilities]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20121014045955/http://www.nationalmuseum.af.mil/factsheets/factsheet.asp?id=1535  WASP Disbanded]\n* [http://www.nationalmuseum.af.mil/factsheets/factsheet.asp?id=1538  WASP Epilogue]\n* [http://www.nationalmuseum.af.mil/factsheets/factsheet.asp?id=5224  Women Pilots with the AAF, 1941\u20131944]\n\n{{US Air Force navbox}}\n{{USWWII}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Women Airforce Service Pilots| ]]\n[[Category:All-female military units and formations]]\n[[Category:American aviators]]\n[[Category:American women in World War II]]\n[[Category:Congressional Gold Medal recipients]]\n[[Category:Female aviators|*]]\n[[Category:Women in the United States military]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n", "name_user": "Kaltenmeyer", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eNotable WASP aviators:clean up, replaced: interiew \u2192 interview", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Women_Airforce_Service_Pilots"}
